{"id": "1458272826602819685", "channel_id": "1439229898475438104", "type": 19, "author_id": "134247328876986369", "author_name": "aegisx", "author_bot": false, "content": "longer than that . since they \"buff\" Ryker SF", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T01:35:35.261000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["481200175566815272"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1458119181156221122", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1439229898475438104", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Who Ryker's Designer pls come talk ?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458369028706930802", "channel_id": "1458369028706930802", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "The description of the Relic \"Foreign Stamp Album\" states it should trigger whenever a \"Non-Awakener Card\" is played, but the actual effect is able to trigger when Corposant's Buff Card \"Pilot\" is played.\n\nEither this is a bug (and it should not trigger), or the definition \"Awakener Card\" should not be used.", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T07:57:51.630000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1458369029084287130", "filename": "screen-20260106-2344482.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 3150063, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458369028706930802/1458369029084287130/screen-20260106-2344482.mp4?ex=69cc273f&is=69cad5bf&hm=e4631144961275561f098a4649dfe229056d1f7c86e10d5a65f93905fba98773&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458369028706930802", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」\"Foreign Stamp Album\" effect does not match description", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1458340548845895781", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 0, "author_id": "672042274275721231", "author_name": "sexysneakystoat1625", "author_bot": false, "content": "The Gmurphy Divine Aequor realm changing idea is a very nice touch to the game. Please, make more characters like that in the future, for other realms too.\n\nI also suggest:\n- some synergy boost effects bonus between Wheels of Destiny. (on same character, or in the whole team)\n- some synergy boost effects bonus between Covenants (or the ability to add 2 covenants on one Character, with some nerf effects maybe)\n- do nerf only when really needed. Imo, **nerf is bad**, **buff is better**. You only have to **nerf characters by buffing enemies/game difficulty**\n- other gameplay boost mechanics, like maybe familiars entities granting bonuses triggering on some conditions in battle or shops. Or Abilities to fuse 2 relics/covenants/Poses into one, other... (when money and business roadmap allows it)\n\nThank you : )", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T06:04:41.502000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❌", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}, {"emoji": "👎", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "IMG_20251113_181453", "emoji_id": "1448240235757568133", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1458340549865242758", "filename": "dsfdssdf.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 20291, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458340548845895781/1458340549865242758/dsfdssdf.JPG?ex=69cc0cb9&is=69cabb39&hm=0bfb4b0e83c57e3b166ec10619ee40db300c632755fe748bb450042ae6b0d9e5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458355051646160997", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 0, "author_id": "640805488757440512", "author_name": "angy_24_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "Sounds overly complicated and puts further load on the players. Gacha players show adverse effects to reading as you may not know.  0/10 do not recommend.", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T07:02:19.239000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458390977034326118", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 0, "author_id": "672042274275721231", "author_name": "sexysneakystoat1625", "author_bot": false, "content": "ah I didn't know.\nI just read it and memorize", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T09:25:04.519000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458398266214449308", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "Synergy boost with specific wheel just limits creativity. One build will be far better than others\nG Murphy Lemurian design is already questionable. No flexibility / customisability, just Lemurian in a team.", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T09:54:02.395000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🫃", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458400308588974164", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 0, "author_id": "967406876029501462", "author_name": "elenakrittik", "author_bot": false, "content": "> do nerf only when really needed. Imo, nerf is bad, buff is better. You only have to nerf characters by buffing enemies/game difficulty\nthis is a very dangerous avenue. it's very hard to come up with a game (or chapter/side story/etc) -wide \"nerf\" (say, mechanic) that only targets one character. spillover is almost certain and can inadvertedly really hurt viability of less optimal comps/builds, and i feel like it should be obvious why requiring perfectly meta comps to clear base game content is a bad idea", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T10:02:09.335000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-07T10:02:25.003000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458401161647362070", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 19, "author_id": "672042274275721231", "author_name": "sexysneakystoat1625", "author_bot": false, "content": "I understand", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T10:05:32.720000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["967406876029501462"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1458400308588974164", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458401184124768308", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 0, "author_id": "672042274275721231", "author_name": "sexysneakystoat1625", "author_bot": false, "content": "all is true", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T10:05:38.079000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458401635637137428", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 19, "author_id": "967406876029501462", "author_name": "elenakrittik", "author_bot": false, "content": "yep. the base system inevitably gets nerfed if the synergy is too good. but i feel like there *is* a small balancing spot where the synergy is good enough to feel real but isn't so much better than the base kits alone that they have to nerf them. hard, but doable i think", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T10:07:25.728000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1458398266214449308", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458404061710778368", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 0, "author_id": "967406876029501462", "author_name": "elenakrittik", "author_bot": false, "content": "> other gameplay boost mechanics, like maybe familiars entities granting bonuses triggering on some conditions in battle or shops. Or Abilities to fuse 2 relics/covenants/Poses into one, other... (when money and business roadmap allows it)\ni think in single-player modes synergies like these are totally fine and the devs can go absolutely crazy with them, because in single-player fun is king and you don't have to worry about balance anywhere as much as in multiplayer modes.\n\nspecial relics or nodes triggering special events when you have certain awakeners/awakener combos in your team would be pretty cool and not really game-breaking imo. even if the special bonus is overpowered, all that happens is \"this particular team comp gets to roll all over the enemies' faces in this side story/chapter/event\", which is typically not a negative (||if it rolls TOO hard then it removes gameplay and thus fun, but in almost all cases you *can* balance it to not be THAT overpowered||) and doesn't impact any system outside of the synergy itself\n\nin the mouchette event we already have a bunch of relics in every stage built-in that synergize with mouchette well and thus make clearing it with mouchette easier than it otherwise would have been, but it makes almost no impact on the viability of non-mouchette comps", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T10:17:04.149000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
