{"id": "1458405139869204545", "channel_id": "1458340548845895781", "type": 0, "author_id": "967406876029501462", "author_name": "elenakrittik", "author_bot": false, "content": "i do like listening to design talk tho so probably picked up a thing or two from there", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T10:21:21.202000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458340548845895781", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Realm's effect/Synergy/Ideas", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1458398518606827520", "channel_id": "1458398518606827520", "type": 0, "author_id": "967406876029501462", "author_name": "elenakrittik", "author_bot": false, "content": "I love these little communications between the characters and Leonora. As insignificant in the grand scheme of things most of those conversations can be, they add so much depth to the characters, makes them feel so much more alive and real. After all, lives don't consist solely of big adventures, right?\n\nThanks so much for this feature, it is absolutely awesome.", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T09:55:02.570000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458398518606827520", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "(feedback) The Inbox is awesome.", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1458368566993748019", "channel_id": "1458368566993748019", "type": 0, "author_id": "257413345450131456", "author_name": "patrueree", "author_bot": false, "content": "Currently the In-Sheath supply daily item expire in 24 hours, making it impossible to stack up the resources for another event more desirable.\n\nI believe it is going to be much more desirable to make it expire only after 7-14 days (or even longer) since it's already much worse than having the \"Special Potion Supply\" item.\n\nThank you!", "timestamp": "2026-01-07T07:56:01.549000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "A_pinch", "emoji_id": "1432980538536493057", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1458368567329296498", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 51076, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458368566993748019/1458368567329296498/image.png?ex=69cc26d1&is=69cad551&hm=7c71480c0f486b7af972e6919bd36e695b5428bf3de1859823633eb9076381ad&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458368566993748019", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "In-Sheath Supply pack possibility of stacking", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
